              🏠 Back to Safety
            </.link>

            <.link
              navigate={~p"/"}
              class="btn btn-outline btn-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-100 text-lg px-8"
            >
              📋 Start Fresh
            </.link>
          </div>
          
<!-- Fun Fact -->
          <div class="mt-8 p-4 bg-orange-50 rounded-lg border border-orange-200">
            <div class="text-sm text-orange-700">
              <strong>🎯 Pro Tip:</strong>
              URLs are like recipes - one wrong ingredient and everything falls apart!
              But hey, at least you found our custom error page. That's more organized than most people's bookmark folders!
              <span class="text-orange-600">📁 Digital tidiness: 2/10</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
<!-- Bonus Section -->
          <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
            <div class="text-xs text-yellow-700 text-center">
              <strong>Fun Fact:</strong>
              This error happens so rarely that our 400 page felt lonely.
              Thanks for visiting! 🎉
            </div>
          </div>
